Class Config

    • se.code77.jq.config.Config
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AndroidConfig

    public abstract class Config
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration for JQ. The configuration offers integration points into the host environment, as well as tweaking of behaviour.

      • monitorUnterminated

        public final boolean monitorUnterminated
        Set to true if unterminated promise chains should cause warnings to be logged. An unterminated promise chain is a chain of promises ending with a promise that has produced a result (fulfilled or rejected) without anyone observing it and without explicitly terminating the chain with Promise.done().
